## Summary / Tóm Tắt

This **Frontend App Router & Navigation Specialist** document covers 20 patterns (9.21-9.40) for Next.js 15 App Router with Feature-Sliced Design:

### Patterns Covered / Các Mẫu Được Bao Gồm

1. **Router Setup** (9.21): Root layout, metadata, provider configuration
2. **Route Configuration** (9.22): Type-safe route definitions with Vietnamese labels
3. **Route Guards** (9.23): Middleware for authentication and authorization
4. **Route Loading** (9.24): Suspense boundaries and skeleton UI
5. **Route Error Handling** (9.25): Error boundaries at route level
6. **Navigation Bar** (9.26): Top navigation with user menu
7. **Sidebar** (9.27): Collapsible side navigation with route groups
8. **Breadcrumbs** (9.28): Breadcrumb navigation for hierarchy
9. **Tab Navigation** (9.29): Tabbed interface for content organization
10. **Mobile Navigation** (9.30): Bottom navigation for mobile devices
11. **Auth Guard** (9.31): Authentication route protection
12. **Role Guard** (9.32): Role-based access control
13. **Permission Guard** (9.33): Permission-based access control
14. **Subscription Guard** (9.34): Subscription-level protection
15. **Maintenance Guard** (9.35): Maintenance mode support
16. **Root Layout** (9.36): App shell structure
17. **App Shell** (9.37): Global layout with header/sidebar/footer
18. **Global Header** (9.38): Global header component
19. **Global Footer** (9.39): Global footer component
20. **Global Styles** (9.40): Global CSS with Tailwind utilities

### Key Features / Các Tính Năng Chính

- Complete Next.js 15 App Router implementation
- Vietnamese legal domain routing (contracts, documents, cases)
- Multi-level access control (auth, role, permission, subscription)
- Bilingual UI (Vietnamese / English)
- Mobile-responsive navigation
- SEO metadata generation
- Type-safe route configuration
- Server Components by default
- Suspense and error boundary patterns
- Comprehensive testing examples

### File Structure / Cấu Trúc Tệp

```
src/
├── app/
│   ├── (auth)/          # Auth routes
│   ├── (dashboard)/     # Dashboard routes
│   ├── (legal)/         # Legal routes
│   ├── (public)/        # Public routes
│   └── layout.tsx       # Root layout
├── widgets/             # Reusable components
│   ├── header/
│   ├── sidebar/
│   ├── breadcrumbs/
│   ├── tabs/
│   ├── footer/
│   └── mobile-nav/
└── shared/config/
    └── routes.ts        # Route configuration
```

