**Specialist Ready**: This document provides production-ready patterns for Frontend App Router & Navigation with Vietnamese legal AI platform focus. All code is TypeScript 5 with strict mode, Next.js 15 conventions, and Feature-Sliced Design principles.

**Version**: 1.0.0 | Next.js 15.3.0 | React 19 | TypeScript 5 | FSD Architecture
